commit.message:
altivec.h [...] (vec_subsubs): Rename to vec_sububs.

2004-04-30  Paolo Bonzini  <bonzini@gnu.org>

        * config/altivec/altivec.h [__cplusplus] (vec_subsubs): Rename to
        vec_sububs.
        [__cplusplus] (vec_subsuhs): Rename to vec_subuhs, without
        duplicates.

From-SVN: r81331
